// Usage:
//   node scripts/check-acp-handshake.mjs <command> [args...] [--timeout <ms>]
//
// Spawns the given ACP agent and runs the two-step handshake the bridge
// performs on every session start: initialize + session/new. Reports
// whether each step succeeds and prints any stderr from the agent.
//
// Exit codes:
//   0  handshake OK (both initialize + session/new returned successfully)
//   1  handshake failed (JSON-RPC error, timeout, or spawn error)
//   2  bad usage
//
// Examples (PowerShell / cmd / bash all the same):
//   node scripts/check-acp-handshake.mjs kiro-cli acp
//   node scripts/check-acp-handshake.mjs codex-acp
//   node scripts/check-acp-handshake.mjs gemini --experimental-acp
